QuestData.Title: Report to Thork
QuestData.Description: Now that the threat here has been stilled, you should return to the Crossroads. Thork would like to speak to you.$B$BFarewell, friend.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Thork at the Crossroads in the Northern Barrens.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Report to Thork at the Crossroads in the Northern Barrens.
QuestData.RewardText: Hello $n. I have heard of your deeds from Darsok. You are a valuable $c of the Horde, indeed.
